This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and annotation of tweets. It could also belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as it deals with data collected from Twitter. Additionally, it could belong to cs.CY (Computers and Society) as it deals with the issue of harassment on social media. It could also belong to cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) as it deals with social behavior on social media. Finally, it could belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as it deals with the issue of cyberbullying and harassment.
